    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">Led office operations and multi-city teams in Romania</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 00-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 000-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">Project and program leadership in complex software environments</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">Governance mindset: KPIs, risk management, accountability</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 border border-zinc-700/50 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem] leading-relaxed">AI-enabled operations for speed and clarity</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-400 text-[0.875rem]">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-zinc-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
      <span>Timisoara (HQ). Available for Arad, Sibiu.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2 class="text-[1.25rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-5">Built for companies scaling into Europe</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-zinc-400 text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-zinc-300 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        European and US companies building EU delivery capacity
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-zinc-300 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        Regulated or quality-critical industries (including healthcare and medicine)
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-zinc-300 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        Scale-ups that need predictable execution without a full local leadership stack
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-800/60 border border-zinc-700/40 px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-zinc-500">
      <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
      Not limited to automotive.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
