<div class="space-y-14">
  <div>
    <p class="text-[0.6875rem] font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-steel uppercase mb-3">About</p>
    <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] lg:text-[2rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-3 leading-tight">
      Built on 15+ years of delivery leadership in Romania
    </h2>
    <p class="text-slate text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
      BMP is led by a Managing Director and shareholder with direct experience building and running engineering subsidiaries in Romania for German technology companies.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-surface border border-divider rounded-md p-8 space-y-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight">Track record</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">Managing Director, 2 subsidiaries</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Full P&amp;L responsibility for Romanian engineering subsidiaries of German parent companies, across multiple cities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">Office ramp-ups in 3 Romanian cities</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Built engineering teams from zero in Timisoara, Cluj, and Iasi — recruiting, onboarding, and establishing delivery operations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">+5M EUR annual operation</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Grew a 20-engineer subsidiary with repeat business from key accounts and consistent on-time delivery across OEM programs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 00-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 000-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">10 years at a global Tier 1</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Cross-functional program leadership (SW, HW, Mechanical, Manufacturing, Quality, Sales) from acquisition through production launch.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">AI-enabled operations</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Currently leading AI integration into development workflows — applying the same tools to accelerate recruiting, governance, and reporting at BMP.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-md bg-steel-light flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-foreground text-[0.875rem] font-medium">Active BOT delivery</p>
          <p class="text-slate text-[0.8125rem] leading-relaxed">Currently executing a Build-Operate-Transfer engagement expanding an engineering services company into mechanical engineering.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-surface border border-divider rounded-md p-8 space-y-4">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground tracking-tight">Domain expertise</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">Embedded Software</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">Automotive (ASPICE, ISO 26262)</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">Mechanical Engineering</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">Android</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">Safety-critical Systems</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-steel-light border border-divider rounded text-[0.8125rem] text-slate">PRINCE2 / Agile</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h3 class="text-[1.25rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-5">Built for companies scaling into Europe</h3>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate text-[0.9375rem] leading-relaxed mb-6">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-foreground shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        European and US companies building EU engineering capacity
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-foreground shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        Regulated or quality-critical industries — automotive, embedded systems, and beyond
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-foreground shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
        Scale-ups that need predictable execution without a full local leadership stack
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-slate text-[0.875rem]">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-steel" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
      <span>Timisoara (HQ). Available across West Romania.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
